From: conda-forge
Subject: [PATCH] Support OpenUSD 26.03+ ARCH_PRAGMA_DEPRECATED rename

OpenUSD 26.03 renamed ARCH_PRAGMA_DEPRECATED_POSIX_NAME to
ARCH_PRAGMA_DEPRECATED (identical body, disables MSVC C4996). The old
name no longer exists in pxr/base/arch/pragmas.h, so use a feature test
to remain compatible with both <26 and >=26.03.

--- a/source/core/python/bindings/NameAlgoBindings.h
+++ b/source/core/python/bindings/NameAlgoBindings.h
@@ -601,6 +601,10 @@

     // FUTURE: Remove when the deprecated ValidChildNameCache class is removed
     ARCH_PRAGMA_PUSH
+#if defined(ARCH_PRAGMA_DEPRECATED_POSIX_NAME)
     ARCH_PRAGMA_DEPRECATED_POSIX_NAME
+#else
+    ARCH_PRAGMA_DEPRECATED
+#endif

     ::class_<ValidChildNameCache>(
         m,
